com.tomzhu.tree

Class BTree<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tomzhu.tree.BTree<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of element.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Tree

    public class BTree<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Tree
    a simple implementation of btree. this btree cannot save duplicate item so must promise that no duplicate item exist. if really want to save duplicate item , you'd better change this implementation. a simply way may be add a property implies the times of the data.
    Since:
    1.7
    Author:
    tomzhu
